snippet.title: [G-Star 2024 Announcement] Dinkum Together Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
We proudly present Dinkum Together, a pioneer life simulation game packed with things to see, play, and create! 
And here’s the big news: Dinkum Together will be featured at South Korea's largest game show, G-Star 2024. 
Come get a first look at Dinkum Together at G-Star!🌟 
※ This video is from the development stage.
👉 Krafton G-Star Website: https://www.krafton.com/gstar2024

🦘 Dinkum Together Official Channels 🦘 
👉 Website: https://dinkum.news/WEB 
👉 YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@DinkumTogether

#Dinkumtogether #Dinkum #Krafton #Trailer #Gameshow
